{"3917030": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "星際調酒師 Cosmic Cocktails", "steam_appid": 3917030, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "detailed_description": "<h1>🔥❤️ ADD OUR NEW GAMES TO WISHLIST ❤️🔥</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3917030/extras/af3ee1e09dcd1cc77f97b3ec71815db7.poster.avif?t=1774442870\" width=622 height=226 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3917030/extras/af3ee1e09dcd1cc77f97b3ec71815db7.webm?t=1774442870\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3917030/extras/af3ee1e09dcd1cc77f97b3ec71815db7.mp4?t=1774442870\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></p><br><h1>關於此遊戲</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3917030/extras/244e30d9d8538330c77cb78e45a3c6df.avif?t=1774442870\" width=1200 height=603 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >歡迎來到銀河中最具氛圍的酒吧——普羅米修斯-9，隱藏於遙遠星區被遺忘的群星之中。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你是這座宇宙避風港的調酒師兼老闆，在這裡，流浪者、賞金獵人、戀人、逃亡者與神秘的外星生命的命運交織在一起——其中有些稀有到連中央指揮部都從未聽說過。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3917030/extras/2d763ae22c1daf63e309d4fdcf44bc81.avif?t=1774442870\" width=1200 height=98 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >透過混合來自銀河各處的異域原料調製獨特的雞尾酒，看看每一杯酒如何影響客人的情緒、誠實度，甚至人生決定。畢竟，每位來訪者不只是來喝一杯，他們帶著故事——以及一個或許、只是或許你能幫助解決的問題。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3917030/extras/20d06b26301177cbe7de1abe2adf5175.poster.avif?t=1774442870\" width=1170 height=560 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3917030/extras/20d06b26301177cbe7de1abe2adf5175.webm?t=1774442870\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3917030/extras/20d06b26301177cbe7de1abe2adf5175.mp4?t=1774442870\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >沉浸在深度對話中，每一次選擇都可能改變事件的發展軌跡。與關鍵角色建立關係——包括來自不同世界與物種的女性——見證她們從隨意的調情發展到跨越星際距離的真摯浪漫。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3917030/extras/358686a3b92b9591c45f2fb0aa765d04.avif?t=1774442870\" width=1200 height=550 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >升級你的酒吧，解鎖新配方，用獨特的物品裝飾空間，將普羅米修斯-9打造成銀河中最特別、最難忘靈魂的避難所。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3917030/extras/2d763ae22c1daf63e309d4fdcf44bc81.avif?t=1774442870\" width=1200 height=98 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >遊戲特色：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✨ 設定於宇宙邊緣的氛圍視覺小說</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >❤️ 來自銀河各地的 6 位獨特女性可建立關係</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✨ 4 位可以深入交往的配角</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >❤️ 使用異域原料的獨特調酒機制</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✨ 多線劇情，擁有多個走向與結局</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >❤️ 酒吧發展與自訂——購買新原料並裝飾內部</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>", "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shar